SUBENT        F0795001   20251225   20260311   20260311       F107
BIB                 10         14
TITLE      Study of the 19F(p,gamma)20Ne radiative capture
           reaction from 0.2-1.2 MeV
AUTHOR     (K.M.Subotic,R.Ostojic,B.Z.Stepancic)
INSTITUTE  (3SRBBKB)
REFERENCE  (J,NP/A,331,491,1979)
FACILITY   (CCW,3SRBBKB) The 1.5 MV.
DETECTOR   (NAICR) 7.6*7.6 cm NaI(TI) crystal.
           (GELI) 24 cm3 and 36 cm3 Ge(Li) detectors.
SAMPLE     The targets were prepared by evaporating CaF2 onto
           copper foil.
METHOD     (GSPEC)
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-S) Statistical error
HISTORY    (20061120C)
           (20251225U) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
ENDBIB              14
COMMON               1          3
ERR-S
PER-CENT
 10.
ENDCOMMON            3
